msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"There is [[!tails_ticket 5563 desc=\"currently\"]] no virtual keyboard in\n"
"<span class=\"application\">Tails Greeter</span>, so a hardware keylogger\n"
"could record your persistent volume passphrase or administration\n"
"password.\n"
msgstr ""

